00:06.005 --> 00:09.926
- THE MOMENT WE'VE ALL BEEN
WAITING FOR IS FINALLY HERE.

00:10.009 --> 00:12.595
TONIGHT,
ON THE MOST DRAMATIC EPISODE

00:12.679 --> 00:15.473
IN THE HISTORY OF THIS SERIES--

00:15.557 --> 00:19.227
- YOU DON'T HAVE TO SHOUT.
I'M RIGHT HERE.

00:19.310 --> 00:21.229
- I'M SORRY, JOY.
UM, LOOK...

00:21.312 --> 00:23.606
YOU'RE ABOUT TO EMBARK
ON AN INCREDIBLE JOURNEY.

00:23.690 --> 00:25.108
TELL US ABOUT IT.

00:25.191 --> 00:27.444
- WELL, EVERY YEAR,
FOR OUR FAKE BIRTHDAYS,

00:27.527 --> 00:29.487
MY FRIENDS AND I FIX
EACH OTHER UP.

00:29.571 --> 00:33.324
- FOUR WOMEN, FOUR DATES.
THERE'S A CHANCE NO ONE'S HEART

00:33.408 --> 00:35.660
IS GONNA BE BROKEN HERE.
WHERE'S THE FUN IN THAT?

00:35.744 --> 00:38.913
- OH, THERE'S ALWAYS PLENTY
OF HEARTBREAK.

00:38.997 --> 00:40.415
