TO BE DIFFERENT.

00:40.498 --> 00:42.250
- DO YOU SAY THAT EVERY YEAR?

00:42.333 --> 00:43.585
- YES.

00:43.668 --> 00:45.962
BUT THIS YEAR REALLY
IS GOING TO BE DIFFERENT.

00:46.045 --> 00:48.631
- DO YOU ALSO SAY THAT
EVERY YEAR?

00:48.715 --> 00:50.925
- YES.

00:51.009 --> 00:52.594
- JUST TELL ME ABOUT THE DATES.

00:52.677 --> 00:56.306
- WELL, ELKA WANTED US TO TRACK
DOWN STAN, HER FIRST LOVE,

00:56.389 --> 00:58.808
WHO SHE LEFT BEHIND IN POLAND
70 YEARS AGO.

00:58.892 --> 01:02.645
- HE WAS MR. SOUR CREAM
WHEN I WAS MISS TEEN POTATO.

01:06.232 --> 01:09.027
WHEN THE VILLAGERS
LAID HIM ON TOP OF ME

01:09.110 --> 01:11.196
AND WRAPPED US IN TINFOIL...

01:11.279 --> 01:16.826
WELL,
ONE THING LED TO ANOTHER.

01:16.910 --> 01:19.162
- SO, WHAT KIND OF RITUAL
IS THAT?

01:19.245 --> 01:23.374
- WELL, IT WAS SUPPOSED
TO KEEP THE GERMANS AWAY.

01:23.458 --> 01:27.253
