WE SHOULD'VE INVESTED IN TANKS.

01:29.798 --> 01:32.383
- VICTORIA WANTED US TO SET
HER UP WITH A MALE MODEL

01:32.467 --> 01:34.719
SHE SAW IN <i> CLEVELAND MAGAZINE.</i>

01:34.803 --> 01:38.014
- WELL, I DON'T CARE ABOUT
ROMANCE. ALL I WANT IS BEAUTY.

01:38.097 --> 01:40.183
- YOU SAY THAT EVERY YEAR.

01:40.266 --> 01:42.685
- YEAH, WELL, I HAVE YET
TO GET IT.

01:42.769 --> 01:46.022
I HAVE PUT UP WITH MAN BOOBS,
CONJOINED TWINS...

01:46.105 --> 01:49.692
