- OH, MY GOD, DO YOU MEAN YOU--

01:58.785 --> 02:00.703
- HEY, YOU KNOW, UH,
WHY DON'T YOU JUST TELL ME ABOUT

02:00.787 --> 02:02.205
THE DATE WITH MELANIE.

02:02.288 --> 02:05.416
- WELL, SHE WANTED A GUY
WHO CALLED INTO HER RADIO SHOW,

02:05.500 --> 02:08.377
LOOKING FOR ADVICE FOR
HIS SHYNESS WITH WOMEN.

02:08.461 --> 02:10.213
- SO, I TOLD HIM TO SEE
A COUNSELOR.

02:10.295 --> 02:12.882
AND THEN, A WEEK LATER,
HE CALLS BACK OFF THE AIR

02:12.966 --> 02:15.051
AND HE WAS JUST SO GRATEFUL
AND SWEET,

02:15.134 --> 02:16.719
AND INCREDIBLY PERCEPTIVE.

02:16.803 --> 02:18.429
- WHAT EXACTLY DID HE SAY?

02:18.513 --> 02:20.014
- HE SAID I WAS BEAUTIFUL
AND SMART.

02:20.098 --> 02:22.225
[murmurs of agreement]

02:22.308 --> 02:24.894
- WELL, I WISH YOU LUCK
WITH YOUR DESPERATE

02:24.978 --> 02:27.272
LITTLE DATING CAPERS.

02:27.355 --> 02:29.065
I, OF COURSE,
WILL BE WITH MITCH,

02:29.149 --> 02:31.734
THE MAN I LOVE, AND WHO,
IN AN UNUSUAL TWIST,

02:31.818 --> 02:34.028
LOVES ME BACK.

02:34.112 --> 02:35.697
SO, DON'T EVEN BOTHER
WISHING ME LUCK,

02:35.780 --> 02:39.576
BECAUSE, FOR ONCE IN MY LIFE,
I DON'T NEED IT.

02:39.659 --> 02:41.369
- SO YOU RUBBED IT IN
YOUR FRIENDS' FACES

02:41.452 --> 02:43.454
BY SAYING YOU HAD
THE PERFECT DATE.

02:43.538 --> 02:45.248
AND THEN YOU TEMPTED FATE
BY SAYING

02:45.331 --> 02:48.084
NOTHING COULD POSSIBLY
GO WRONG FOR YOU.

02:48.167 --> 02:51.754
IN RETROSPECT,
YOU WISH YOU HADN'T DONE THAT?

02:51.838 --> 02:55.758
- I DO.
I REALLY DO.

