03:16.237 --> 03:17.906
{\an8}- OH.
[both laugh]

03:17.989 --> 03:19.616
{\an8}BRIAN,
I'M HAVING SUCH A GOOD TIME.

03:19.699 --> 03:22.911
{\an8}- OH, ME TOO. THE WORLD...

03:22.994 --> 03:24.746
{\an8}DISAPPEARS WHEN I LOOK AT YOU.

03:24.829 --> 03:26.748
{\an8}- OH, BRIAN.

03:26.831 --> 03:28.750
{\an8}SOMEONE'S GOTTEN
OVER THEIR SHYNESS, HUH?

03:28.833 --> 03:30.084
{\an8}- [laughs]

03:30.168 --> 03:32.795
{\an8}- OH, SORRY I'M LATE.
HOW ARE THINGS GOING?

03:32.879 --> 03:35.506
{\an8}- UH, GREAT, I THINK. UH,
THINGS ARE GOING GREAT, RIGHT?

03:39.552 --> 03:41.679
{\an8}- I--YEAH.
UM, BRIAN, WHO IS THIS?

03:41.763 --> 03:43.681
{\an8}- I'M SORRY,
MELANIE, THIS IS MARCY.

03:43.765 --> 03:47.685
{\an8}- OH, SO NICE TO MEET YOU.
HAVE YOU TOUCHED HER YET?

03:47.769 --> 03:51.522
{\an8}- I'VE HELD HER HAND. MM-HM.
- GOOD, GOOD, THAT'S VERY GOOD.

03:51.606 --> 03:53.191
{\an8}ANY COMPLIMENTS?
- WELL, I DID THE ONE ABOUT

03:53.274 --> 03:55.151
{\an8}THE WORLD DISAPPEARING.
- OH, EXCELLENT.

03:55.234 --> 03:56.778
{\an8}- YEAH.

03:56.861 --> 03:59.697
{\an8}- UH, SORRY, I STILL DON'T KNOW
WHO MARCY IS.

03:59.781 --> 04:02.951
{\an8}- OH, OH. WHEN YOU ADVISED
ME TO GET PROFESSIONAL HELP,

04:03.034 --> 04:04.160
{\an8}MARCY IS THE PERSON I CALLED.

04:04.243 --> 04:06.454
- OH, SHE'S YOUR THERAPIST.

04:06.537 --> 04:08.915
