HELP SOMEONE OUT.

05:28.619 --> 05:30.580
- ARE YOU DONATING A KIDNEY
TO SOMEONE?

05:30.663 --> 05:33.124
- NO, UH, MY BROTHER
WAS IN A CAR ACCIDENT

05:33.207 --> 05:36.461
AND HIS NOSE
WAS IRREPARABLY DAMAGED.

05:36.544 --> 05:40.465
WELL, FOREHEAD SKIN IS THE BEST
MATCH FOR NOSE SKIN.

05:40.548 --> 05:44.469
- SO...YOU'RE DONATING
SOME OF YOUR PERFECT

05:44.552 --> 05:47.305
