- EVEN BETTER.

05:47.388 --> 05:51.934
THIS IS REALLY GONNA
MAKE YOU HAPPY.

05:52.018 --> 05:54.395
IMPRESSIVE, HUH?

06:01.652 --> 06:05.448
- WELL, IT'S NOTHING
TO SNEEZE AT.

06:05.531 --> 06:09.077
- IT WAS SO ROMANTIC OF YOU
TO RESERVE THE WHOLE PATIO

06:09.160 --> 06:11.913
JUST FOR US.

06:11.996 --> 06:14.957
MITCH, ARE YOU OKAY?

06:15.041 --> 06:18.252
- JOY, I'VE BEEN THINKING A LOT
ABOUT THE TWO OF US

06:18.336 --> 06:22.048
