OTHER AND ABOUT OUR FUTURE.

06:22.131 --> 06:25.968
- FUTURE? ARE YOU SAYING
WHAT I THINK YOU'RE SAYING?

06:26.052 --> 06:27.470
- PLEASE, I WANT TO GET THIS
JUST RIGHT.

06:27.553 --> 06:31.474
- SORRY, GO AHEAD.

06:31.557 --> 06:34.644
- OKAY, UH, WHERE WAS I?

06:34.727 --> 06:36.145
THINKING ABOUT THE TWO OF US...

06:36.229 --> 06:37.814
