06:47.907 --> 06:49.659
- JOY, WILL YOU MARRY ME?

06:52.370 --> 06:55.456
- WHAT THE HELL?

06:55.540 --> 06:58.501
- SIMON, DID YOU
JUST PROPOSE TO ME?

06:58.584 --> 07:00.002
- YES, I DID.
- WELL, SO DID I.

07:00.086 --> 07:01.671
