ANYMORE.

07:38.457 --> 07:40.376
- TWO MEN JUST PROPOSED TO ME.

07:40.459 --> 07:42.670
FIRST MITCH, AND THEN SIMON!

07:42.753 --> 07:45.590
- OH, MY GOD, JOY!
- I KNOW!

07:45.673 --> 07:48.050
TWO WONDERFUL, HANDSOME MEN
WHO WANT TO SPEND

07:48.134 --> 07:49.677
THE REST OF THEIR LIVES
WITH ME.

07:49.760 --> 07:51.888
OH, THIS IS ALL SO COMPLICATED.

07:51.971 --> 07:55.057
- THERE'S ONLY ONE THING
MORE COMPLICATED.

07:55.141 --> 07:56.893
