A LITTLE SAME-SPOT-SALLY.

09:05.211 --> 09:07.421
- YOU KNOW WHAT? I THINK THE TWO
OF US CAN TAKE IT FROM HERE.

09:07.505 --> 09:10.174
- OH! OKAY.
- UH...

09:10.258 --> 09:13.094
- DON'T BE NERVOUS.
