SERVE HUMANITY.

10:14.905 --> 10:17.033
- I--I'M SORRY, WHAT?

10:17.116 --> 10:19.285
- YEAH, SEE THIS LITTLE GUY
RIGHT HERE?

10:21.537 --> 10:22.705
