OF YOU SEPARATELY?

12:41.802 --> 12:44.680
- MAY THE BEST MAN WIN.
- OR THE FUNNIEST.

12:44.763 --> 12:48.559
- OR THE TALLEST AND SMARTEST
AND HANDSOMEST.

12:48.642 --> 12:51.854
