AND SMARTEST.

12:58.944 --> 13:02.198
- SO, YOU'RE STILL CONSIDERING
ALL THREE OF THEM, EVEN BOB?

13:02.281 --> 13:05.534
- YES, EVEN BOB.
I LIKE HIM.

13:05.618 --> 13:09.497
- AND HE LIKES YOU.
WHICH PUTS HIM AHEAD OF MY DATE,

13:09.580 --> 13:11.540
